{"tid":1615083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依個陰濕youtuber一路扮中立一路屌示威者","createTime":"2019-10-03T03:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T04:19:04.000Z","uid":114550,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"04713a8ebbac6e9db61545cce2f7c9953116e68b","tid":1615083,"uid":114550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SabfWKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSabfWKC.png&h=7c393a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早幾日無意上youtube睇到，一開頭以為真係中立，越睇就越唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />滿口都歪理，講野同警察一撚樣。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>啲假設全部都係幫藍絲</strong></span>最後仲要懶係關心大家，好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />私了播就播垃圾TVB最有爭議性個條，明抹黑我地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好話屌，係人都知佢戇鳩，我同你講啲懶高級藍絲係好撚受落，你睇下啲留言就知。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R7BWGcc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR7BWGcc.png&h=5e7dbfa9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rYdFoqy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrYdFoqy.png&h=ccbf70bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設同我講乜撚野黑衣人企喺狗屋出面大叫 光復香港 會冇事？屌你問你有冇良心都俾啲狗扑頭拉撚左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有太多可以反駁既位，你地睇完就明，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫幫手，入去dislike同report，</span></span>唔好俾依啲人亂帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同我推爆個post呀！<br />\n<br />\n上youtube打Chongsan就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8291e18fbf00bc1be1335e398bade5d5ae2fff06","tid":1615083,"uid":114550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"53f4e75a8214bec39ce5baccbad47d218f86d131","tid":1615083,"uid":25